1
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,560
I'll go give this red string

2
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,360
to my sister Xingyao later,

3
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,620
and say goodbye to her.

4
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,800
Your sister is an ominous person.

5
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,000
How can you see her before your wedding?

6
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:05,240
Xingyao.

7
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,380
Why are you locked up here?

8
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:17,120
Aren't you

9
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,920
already dead?

10
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,320
How are you still alive?

11
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:21,960
I didn't

12
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,680
kill you.

13
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,800
It wasn't me.

14
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:28,400
It was the Eldest Princess.

15
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,450
What exactly

16
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,320
is going on?

17
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,050
It was the Eldest Princess.

18
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,040
She said

19
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,440
she'd help me kill you

20
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:42,360
and let me take your place as the Empress.

21
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,880
She said

22
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:47,120
she could help me remove my birthmark,

23
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:51,360
and then give me back my freedom.

24
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,960
In that case,

25
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,440
because the original Cangyue was already dead,

26
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,480
I accidentally came to this world.

27
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,400
But,

28
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,000
after I came to Donglin,

29
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,120
she said,

30
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:14,000
she said my resentment was too deep,

31
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:17,079
perfect for raising the most poisonous Gu.

32
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,320
So I was locked up here.

33
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,520
Resentment.

34
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,880
So you hated

35
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:33,800
my parents to the bone,

36
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,079
so much that you'd sacrifice

37
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,680
the lives of our entire clan?

38
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,930
What are you talking about?

39
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:43,360
What lives of the entire clan?

40
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,040
They are all dead.

41
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,720
As far as the eye could see,

42
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,220
corpses littered the fields.

43
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,160
How is that possible?

44
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,640
How could this be?

45
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,720
I didn't mean it.

46
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:03,920
I really didn't mean it.

47
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,000
Since I am the one

48
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,160
who caused all this...

49
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,640
Then let me

50
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,680
end this.

51
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,000
Xingyao, what are you doing?

52
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,360
Don't do anything stupid.

53
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,000
There must be another way to solve this.

54
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,120
Xingyao!

55
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,880
Sister!

56
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:35,080
The Jiuyin Gu is refined with human blood.

57
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,720
They are born as a mother-child pair.

58
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:41,360
The mother and child Gu are placed in two people's bodies.

59
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,840
The child Gu absorbs life essence

60
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,159
to supply the mother Gu to release venom.

61
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,000
The only solution

62
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,760
is to take the child Gu.

63
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,730
The host of the child Gu must be killed.

64
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,520
Otherwise,

65
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,620
they will never die

66
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,480
or perish.

67
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,490
Xingyao,

68
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,930
don't be impulsive.

69
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,580
There must be another way.

70
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,660
Let me get you out first, Xingyao.

71
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,520
Only if I die,

72
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:17,000
can the others infected with the Gu

73
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,640
continue to live.

74
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:23,560
Sister,

75
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,840
I'm sorry.

76
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,400
Xingyao!

77
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,160
Xingyao!

78
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,680
Xingyao!

79
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:46,440
Experiencer's character objective 80% complete.

80
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,840
Xingyao said that in three days at most,

81
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,010
the Gu poison in your body will be cleared.

82
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,960
Grand General Pixiu,

83
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,600
charge!

84
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:13,880
Yan,

85
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,360
how can Pixiu still go to battle?

86
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,680
Even Sleeping Beauty can slay demons.

87
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,600
So Pixiu can go to battle too.

88
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,720
Look, there's also this.

89
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,600
A tiger tally.

90
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,760
Yan, where did this come from?

91
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:37,080
This is a new gift from my brother.

92
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,840
My brother said

93
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,560
that with this, I can deploy troops

94
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,760
and go into battle.

95
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,320
When did His Majesty give it to you?

96
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:47,120
Before my brother went to sleep.

97
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:51,040
It seems Si Xingxuan also noticed something was wrong.

98
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:54,250
He kept a trick up his sleeve before fainting.

99
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:57,860
He isn't stupid enough to be easily brought down by Si Xinglan.

100
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:23,200
I didn't expect the Eldest Princess to have poisoned me so long ago.

101
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:26,800
No wonder I've been extremely irritable at times over the years.

102
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,520
I thought I really was a tyrant.
